Package: pgtgpigpio
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: KD4Z
Depends: libgpiod3
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: TCP/JSON GPIO relay control service
 PgTgPiGpio provides a persistent TCP listener with a JSON API to set,
 clear, and time-limit GPIO relay outputs on a Raspberry Pi 4.
